Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.09,0:00:03.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（影片开始）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.10,0:00:11.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚刚转到这个学校
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.17,0:00:16.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有点期待呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.11,0:00:19.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会不会有什么美好恋情呢？嘻嘻
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.18,0:00:22.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.12,0:00:31.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是转学生
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.12,0:00:35.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请自我介绍
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.13,0:00:39.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.06,0:00:42.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是西宫
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.07,0:00:48.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.07,0:00:52.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.08,0:01:00.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实大家呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.15,0:01:07.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要帮你准备惊喜哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.16,0:01:12.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.16,0:01:15.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.17,0:01:19.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家对我这么好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.17,0:01:23.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办 好高兴哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.07,0:01:55.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么我们开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.14,0:02:00.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.14,0:02:03.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你先过来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.15,0:02:06.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到垫子上
