Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.10,0:02:27.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是干什么呀？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.11,0:02:33.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不太懂呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.18,0:02:36.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我们准备的惊喜哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.11,0:02:39.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.12,0:02:43.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.05,0:02:46.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有点害羞呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.06,0:02:50.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.06,0:02:54.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用害羞呀
