Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.15,0:03:15.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么请吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.11,0:03:44.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.06,0:04:01.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样懂了吗？
